Package gw.document

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DocumentApplicationContext
    Interface for app-independent PCFs to create/manipulate app-specific DocumentCreationInfo and DocumentDetailsApplicationHelper objects

    Should be implemented at the application level
    DocumentApplicationContext.DocumentCreationResetState
    Block for resetting UI specific state during document creation
    DocumentCreationInfo.GlobalContextProducer  
    Symbol
    A symbol used for document generation
    SymbolProvider
    Provids execution context for the document generation
    TemplatePluginUtils.TemplateResultBlock
    This interface is used by the resolveTemplates after the templates have been resolved, it is executed in the target locale.
    TemplatePluginUtils.TemplateSetupBlock
    This interface is used by the resolveTemplates to setup the IScriptHost with the symbols that are required by the templates.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContentDisposition
    Used to specify the type of disposition for file content downloads in configuration: ContentDisposition.DEFAULT, ContentDisposition.INLINE or ContentDisposition.ATTACHMENT
    ContextObject  
    DocumentContentsInfo
    Class encapsulating the response from either a document creation or document retrieval request.
    DocumentCreationInfo
    Encapsulates information about a Document entity currently being created in the UI.
    DocumentCreationInfo.DynamicWidgetInfo
    Wrapper object which corresponds to a context object whose value must be chosen by the user when creating a document from a document template.
    DocumentDetailsApplicationHelper
    Base class for platform PCFs to manipulate application-defined LVs/DVs Should be extended at the application level for all LV/DV cells/inputs
    DocumentDetailsInfo
    Encapsulates information about a Document entity whose details are being displayed on the document details UI page.
    DocumentsUtil
    Document-related methods used in the ClaimCenter UI.
    DocumentsUtilBase
    Helper methods for the Document-related UI pages.
    GosuCaseInsensitiveBackwardsCompatibleSymbolProvider
    Simple symbol provider that accepts a Map
    LocationSymbolProvider  
    SimpleSymbol
    A simple symbol that directly stores the type and value
    SimpleSymbolProvider
    Simple symbol provider that accepts a Map
    TemplatePluginUtils
    Class to hold a number of utility methods common to Document, Email, and Note template plugins
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ContentDispositionType
    Used to specify the type of disposition for file content downloads: ContentDispositionType.DEFAULT, ContentDispositionType.INLINE or ContentDispositionType.ATTACHMENT
    DocumentContentsInfo.ContentResponseType
    Enumerated content response type
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DocumentExistsException
    Document Already Exists Exception
